title: NFL Week 11: Updated Playoff Odds & Vikings TE Kyle Rudolph
itunes:title: NFL Week 11: Updated Playoff Odds & Vikings TE Kyle Rudolph
description:
Cynthia Frelund and Matt "Money" Smith use predictive analytics to update their NFL playoff odds and preview the week 11 games, including a huge matchup between the Los Angeles Rams and Minnesota Vikings. Later, Cynthia talks with Vikings TE Kyle Rudolph about the responsibilities of a tight end and how many different QBs he has caught passes from.
